data.name: XInteractionRequestStringResolver
desc: Obtains human readable strings from an XInteractionRequest.

methods.name: getStringFromInformationalRequest
desc: Obtains a string containing a human readable message from an informational interaction request.

An informational interaction request contains not more than one interaction continuation (user has no choice; request is just informational). The supplies continuation must either be a XInteractionAbort or XInteractionApprove
